  "title": "QAQC Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Report non-conformities, perform analysis, identify root cause and propose corrective actions.</li>\n  <li>Conduct independent Quality Assurance check on project site.</li>\n  <li>Identify and assess any potential risk arising from workplace or work processes.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and control QA/QC practices on daily basis with regular check and inspections ensuring correct operation and implementation of procedures;</li>\n  <li>Conduct inspections to in-progress / completed works and ensure Works are in accordance to project specification and approved construction drawings;</li>\n  <li>Monitor corrective actions and process improvement;</li>\n  <li>Manage subcontractors to clear defects and achieve required CONQUAS target.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree holder in Civil Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>At least 3 to 5 years of experience in quality control in local construction project</li>\n  <li>The successful applicant must be resourceful enough to work independently</li>\n  <li>Alternate Satuday work</li>\n</ul>",
